00b22d5c-8793-4812-beb7-c06e21fdf394.title: Dimintheis
00b22d5c-8793-4812-beb7-c06e21fdf394.text:
Hello. My name is Dimintheis, of the noble family
Fitzharmon.

options.text: Why would a nobleman live in a dump like this?
You're rich then? Can I have some money?
Hi, I am a bold adventurer.

8395bcef-74fb-419b-9126-a0a7091a4e5d.title: <player>
8395bcef-74fb-419b-9126-a0a7091a4e5d.text: You're rich then? Can I have some money?

c6c2ac83-d358-4f5b-bc98-a2439c5306c5.title: Dimintheis
c6c2ac83-d358-4f5b-bc98-a2439c5306c5.text:
Gah! Lousy beggar! Your sort is what's ruining this
great land! Why don't you just go and get a job if you
need money so badly?

5813bde3-20c0-4be5-81d8-e5a36791882c.title: <player>
5813bde3-20c0-4be5-81d8-e5a36791882c.text: Why would a nobleman live in a dump like this?

f60350a9-9656-467f-b650-143afbc53dba.title: Dimintheis
f60350a9-9656-467f-b650-143afbc53dba.text:
The King has taken my estate from me until such time
as I can show my family crest to him.

ccb1cc1f-c058-4e44-8c0d-e661fc77ed06.title: <player>
ccb1cc1f-c058-4e44-8c0d-e661fc77ed06.text: Hi, I am a bold adventurer.

f950bd99-d9b2-40fc-9d2c-4d4f032ee9a0.title: Dimintheis
f950bd99-d9b2-40fc-9d2c-4d4f032ee9a0.text:
An adventurer hmmm? How lucky. I may have an
adventure for you. I desperately need my family crest
returning to me. It is of utmost importance.

options.text: Why are you so desperate for it?
I'm not interested in that adventure right now.

b0e4dcf1-9759-4e0c-a4b5-412144becb77.title: <player>
b0e4dcf1-9759-4e0c-a4b5-412144becb77.text: I'm not interested in that adventure right now.

1673acc2-b2c8-4c88-ba9a-26af748bf12a.title: Dimintheis
1673acc2-b2c8-4c88-ba9a-26af748bf12a.text: I realise it was a lot to ask of a stranger.

57cd1de9-f780-4e52-8c5a-997b9122f0cb.title: <player>
57cd1de9-f780-4e52-8c5a-997b9122f0cb.text: Why are you so desperate for it?

e5c1a5c1-1d7b-4c03-a041-f11c51c7727d.title: Dimintheis
e5c1a5c1-1d7b-4c03-a041-f11c51c7727d.text:
Well, there is a long standing rule of chivalry amongst
the Varrockian aristocracy, where each noble family is
in possession of a unique crest, which signifies the
honour and lineage of the family. More than this

849906dc-0d12-4472-8869-0cb3cacfdf9c.title: Dimintheis
849906dc-0d12-4472-8869-0cb3cacfdf9c.text:
however, it also represents the lawful rights of each
family to prove their ownership of their wealth and
lands. If the family crest is lost, then the family's estate
is handed over to the current monarch until the crest is

3388efc3-c5cb-4433-a806-e87f302a1bfb.title: Dimintheis
3388efc3-c5cb-4433-a806-e87f302a1bfb.text:
This dates back to the times when there was much in-
fighting amongst the noble families and their clans, and
was introduced as a way of reducing the bloodshed that
was devestating the ranks of the ruling classes at that

00950eff-64f1-4de8-9c9c-1dcb85815ba5.title: Dimintheis
00950eff-64f1-4de8-9c9c-1dcb85815ba5.text:
time. When you captured a rival family's clan, you also
captured their lands and wealth.

f7e17e32-ccb5-499b-a1de-518920bab43f.title: Dimintheis
f7e17e32-ccb5-499b-a1de-518920bab43f.text:
Well, my three sons took it with them many years ago
when they rode out to fight in the war against the
undead necromancer and his army in the battle to save
Varrock.

b7adc447-0b45-46d3-b0c6-7ed4460ac1ea.title: Dimintheis
b7adc447-0b45-46d3-b0c6-7ed4460ac1ea.text:
For many years I had assumed them all dead, as I had
heard no word from them, but recently I heard word
that my son Caleb is alive and well, and trying to earn
his fortune as a great chef in the lands beyond White

41edfb6a-1193-418b-9ede-e6bff366e01f.title: Dimintheis
41edfb6a-1193-418b-9ede-e6bff366e01f.text: Wolf Mountain, although I know not where.

options.text: I'm not interested in that adventure right now.
